---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection
  title="Streamline your workflows. Expand to new markets. Increase your margins.​"
  id="intro"
>
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="size-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    TwoWay uses your <span class="text-primary">interactions with brokers</span> to bring you all your
    mark-to-markets in <span class="text-primary">real-time</span>
  </Fragment>

  <span class="text-left text-lg" style="margin-top:-32px">
    <br />
  ⏱️ Respond <span class="text-primary">faster</span>, and more precisely to brokers, thus growing your business and
  profitability​
  <br />
  🚧 Spot any <span class="text-primary">pricing gaps</span>, as <span class="text-primary">opportunities</span>, pricing issues, or model risks​
  <br />
  🤖 <span class="text-primary">Streamline</span> all manual pricing, and trade capture, reducing operational risk​
  </span>
</ContentSection>
